This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the task of creating textual descriptions of audio signals, which is a form of natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with audio signals. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) as it involves the creation of a dataset for multi-modal translation. It could also be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it involves crowdsourcing. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as it deals with the creation of a dataset through a framework that involves human input.
